data.description: Check out this FRESHLY PAINTED townhome ready for a new owner.  Enter through the front door into a spacious living/dining room area with a large box window and laminate floors.  As you step towards the rear of the home you have a convenient powder room that doubles as a laundry area with front loading appliances.  The kitchen and family room area boasts a fireplace and vaulted ceilings with skylights that open to the upstairs loft area.  The kitchen has stainless steel appliances, a gas stove and dishwasher.  Walk upstairs to the loft  where you will find a perfect place for a sitting/study area….or whatever your needs may be. The second floor boasts a large master bedroom complete with a walk in closet and master bath.  This bathroom has a soaking tub for those days you need a relaxing bath and a nice separate shower when you are in a rush.  This level is completed with a second bedroom and full hall bath.  The BONUS IN THIS HOME IS A FULL BASEMENT.  Not many townhomes in this development offer a basement that is partially finished and additional room for storage.  All this and a partially fenced in backyard and attached garage with a 2020 new garage door!  Another BONUS, the ROOF IS ONE YEAR OLD,  hot water heater about 4 years young and NO HOA FEES!!   Make your appointment now!
